text:
Every cup of Tapal Tea is made with premium tea leaves; handpicked from the best gardens in the world. 

Tapal Tea has made its mark over 40 destinations including North and South America, Asia, Europe & Africa. We are on a journey to continue bringing to you the finest flavor, color & aroma that makes you fall in love with every sip.

So, here is to cherishing each moment & celebrating this International Tea Day with a cup of Tapal Tea. 

#TapalTea #TrulyYours #InternationalTeaDay

Iss Eid ki mithaas manayein tum, mein aur aik cup chai ke saath!

#EidMubarak #TumMeinAurAikCupChai #TapalDanedar

Which one do you prefer?
#TapalDanedar #TumMeinAurAikCupChai

#Tapal #StayStrongPakistan #HopeBrewsStrong

Take this day to thank your mom for every hug, word of encouragement, and act of love. 
Happy Mother's Day!
#MothersDay #TapalDanedar

Tapal strives to get you quality product while safeguarding the health of our essential workers. 

#Tapal #StayStrongPakistan #HopeBrewsStrong

Pakistan, yeh waqt mushkil hai, tou kya? Aao, hum issay apni taareekh dikhate hain.

#Tapal #StayStrongPakistan #HamariNationalitea

text:
There is nothing like a freshly brewed cup of tea to get you going anytime of the day!
#TapalDanedar #TumMeinAurAikCupChai

Every bit of kindness we can spare for others, makes a huge difference during this tough time. 
Tapal Tea (Pvt) Ltd aims to help those in need by donating hundreds of thousands of tea packs to the charitable organizations.

#Tapal #StayStrongPakistan

Aaj Aik Cup Chai Khud Ke Saath
Taakay Kal Hosakey Tumharey Saath!

#StayHome #TapalDanedar

This 23rd March, let's come together as a nation to conquer tough times, like we've done before.

#TapalDanedar #PakistanResolutionDay

Enjoy the tantalizing taste of Elaichi with your loved ones.
#TapalDanedar #TumMeinAurAikCupChai #TapalDanedarElaichi #KuchToSpecialHai #SpecialChai

Allah Ki Rehmatien hain apki muntazir!

1st Lucky Draw main Umrah ki saadat hasil karne wale 15 khush naseebon ko Tapal Danedar ki taraf se buhat buhat mubarak.

#TapalDanedar #Umrah
